      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se nessun inventario in corso : uscita          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rn-dat-inv-tip-iic   =    spaces
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-pre-exe-pgm
                     go to pre-exe-pgm-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se rilevazione gia' eseguita : uscita           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rn-dat-inv-flg-gdi   not  = spaces
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-pre-exe-pgm
                     go to pre-exe-pgm-999.
